### 收藏功能 HTTP 测试文件

### 前置步骤：先登录获取 token（替换为你的登录接口）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "1",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}

### 1. 收藏知识库文章（需要先登录获取token）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/collections/toggle
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 7,
  "targetId": 1,
  "type": "knowledge",
  "title": "如何识别电信诈骗",
  "summary": "电信诈骗的常见手段和防范方法"
}

### 2. 收藏案例
POST http://localhost:8080/api/collections/toggle
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 7,
  "targetId": 1,
  "type": "case",
  "title": "某大学生被骗案例",
  "summary": "一名大学生因刷单被骗的详细经过"
}

### 3. 检查是否已收藏（知识库）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/collections/check/knowledge/1?userId=7
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 4. 检查是否已收藏（案例）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/collections/check/case/1?userId=7
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 5. 获取用户收藏列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/collections?userId=7
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 6. 取消收藏（通过 toggle 接口再次调用）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/collections/toggle
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 7,
  "targetId": 1,
  "type": "knowledge",
  "title": "如何识别电信诈骗",
  "summary": "电信诈骗的常见手段和防范方法"
}

### 7. 删除指定收藏（通过收藏ID删除）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/collections/1
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### 8. 未认证访问收藏接口（应该失败）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/collections?userId=7

### 9. 测试收藏重复添加（应该自动切换）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/collections/toggle
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "userId": 7,
  "targetId": 2,
  "type": "knowledge",
  "title": "另一个知识库文章",
  "summary": "这是另一篇文章的摘要"
}